item.title: CVE-2024-22388|2024-10-17T18:44:10.399Z -- hid%20global -- iclass%20se%20cp1000%20encoder
item.description: Certain configuration available in the communication channel for encoders could expose sensitive data when reader configuration cards are programmed. This data could include credential and device administration keys.
